data.description: Southside Gem in beautiful Santa Fe! Highly motivated owner says "let's get it sold!" Located just off Jaguar Drive in well-established neighborhood and walking distance from several elementary, middle schools and high schools- the Southside Library, new Teen Center and more! This beautiful 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage home is move-in ready. The entire home is tiled, with brand new appliances, toilets, security system, lights, plumbing fixtures, and new garage door. Prospective homebuyers won't find a more beautifully appointed locale and opportunity. Just 30 minutes from Los Alamos, Albuquerque, and ten minutes from the Santa Fe Plaza and downtown. Seller to credit Buyer up to $5k at successful closing.
